2012;;The Rise and Fall of a White Collar Hooligan;;British;;Director: Paul Tanter;;Director: Paul TanterCast: Nick Nevern, Simon Phillips, Rita Ramnani, Billy Murray;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Rise_and_Fall_of_a_White_Collar_Hooligan;;An unemployed football fanatic named Mike Jacobs (played by Nick Nevern) becomes a major credit card fraudster and gangster. The movie depicts the lifestyles of luxury, frivolous spending and violent reprisals of its criminal underworld. Alongside the main character is Mike's old friend named Eddie (played by Simon Phillips) who introduces Mike into the business of the fraud. There is also the portrayal of Mike's girlfriend Katie (played by Rita Ramnani) who is faithful to Mike but not supportive of Mike's choice of lifestyle.